360
00:36:14,020 --> 00:36:19,010
Eating here with just you makes me feel nostalgic.

361
00:36:19,010 --> 00:36:22,560
Eating the leftover gamjatang with cold rice.

362
00:36:22,560 --> 00:36:27,400
We went out of business as soon as we had a meal.

363
00:36:28,410 --> 00:36:35,290
Now that I think about it, I think I was the happiest back then.

364
00:36:35,290 --> 00:36:40,730
Even though all I had was you and me to depend on in the world,

365
00:36:40,730 --> 00:36:44,130
I never thought I was lonely.

366
00:36:48,870 --> 00:36:52,120
- Stop lying through your teeth.
- What?

367
00:36:52,120 --> 00:36:56,910
You weren't lonely because of me, it was because of someone else.

368
00:37:00,030 --> 00:37:03,250
