438
00:42:44,410 --> 00:42:48,100
You bastard...

439
00:42:48,100 --> 00:42:52,870
- Honey, I was wrong. Let's hurry up and go home, okay?
- Okay!

440
00:42:54,070 --> 00:42:56,490
Wow!

441
00:42:56,490 --> 00:43:00,500
Goodbye, everyone!

442
00:43:03,600 --> 00:43:05,550
Goodbye!

443
00:43:05,600 --> 00:43:10,600
Everyone! That's my father! Dondon F&B's CEO!

444
00:43:10,600 --> 00:43:13,000
