447
00:43:29,670 --> 00:43:33,750
I said not to bring up Cheongsong in front of me, didn't I?

448
00:43:33,750 --> 00:43:38,600
I thought you could swing by since you have business in that area.

449
00:44:16,360 --> 00:44:18,170
What is it?

450
00:44:19,500 --> 00:44:23,800
It's nothing, I just imagined I saw something right now.

451
00:44:30,650 --> 00:44:35,300
I guess the Cheongsong art camp this time will be held without the director.

452
00:44:35,300 --> 00:44:37,340
Won't it be difficult to get back to Korea before that?

453
00:44:37,340 --> 00:44:42,030
