569
00:51:53,490 --> 00:51:58,030
I am going to let a corrupt cop like you taste a free prison meal so that you can come to your senses.

570
00:51:59,350 --> 00:52:02,090
Wait... What was 112 again?

571
00:52:02,090 --> 00:52:04,090
Shall I call and ask 114?

572
00:52:04,090 --> 00:52:05,980
Is she a female version of Jin Moo Hak or something?

573
00:52:05,980 --> 00:52:08,830
